Description: A comprehensive analytical framework for Africa's Global Value Chain (GVC) 
    readiness diagnostics with elite publication-ready outputs. Provides comparative 
    analysis across Africa, LAC, ASEAN, OECD, and China as distinct regions with 
    0-1 normalized indicators, advanced visualizations, and policy-relevant insights.
